column2: SELECT DR7.objID,DR7.ra,DR7.dec, DR7.psfMag_u, DR7.psfMag_g, DR7.psfMag_r, DR7.psfMag_i, DR7.psfMag_z, DR7.dered_u, DR7.dered_g, DR7.dered_r, DR7.dered_i, DR7.dered_z,   DR7.extinction_u, DR7.extinction_g, DR7.extinction_r, DR7.extinction_i, DR7.extinction_z into mydb.MyTable_success FROM PhotoObjAll as DR7 JOIN daniela AS dani   ON DR7.ra = dani.ra   AND DR7.dec = dani.dec
